            "title": "盤中速報 - 好市多(COST-US)大跌5.03%，報974.98美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>好市多(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COST:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COST\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COST-US</a>)截至台北時間07日22:36股價下跌51.65美元，報974.98美元，跌幅5.03%，成交量420,384（股），盤中最高價1002.42美元、最低價974.19美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.13%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.08%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.04%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.68%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>好市多(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COST:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COST\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COST-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2.55%</li> <li>近 1 月：-0.31%</li> <li>近 3 月：+5.56%</li> <li>近 6 月：+19.51%</li> <li>今年以來：+14.35%</li></ul></section></main>",
